@startuml
!theme plain
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 150

actor "Nutzer" as User
participant "Angular Frontend\n(Giro3D & WebWorker)" as UI
participant "Core API (Backend)" as Backend
database "PostgreSQL\n(PostGIS)" as DB

User -> UI : Öffnet Experiment 3D-View
UI -> Backend : GET /experiment/123/model
Backend --> UI : Return IFC-File (inkl. Sensor-IDs)

UI -> UI : WebWorker parst und rendert IFC-Geometrie

loop Für jeden referenzierten Sensor
    UI -> Backend : GET /sensor/{id}/metadata
    Backend -> DB : Fetch Details (Typ, Name, Status)
    DB --> Backend : Result
    Backend --> UI : Return Metadata
    UI -> UI : Verknüpft Metadaten mit 3D-Objekt (Hover-Overlays)
end

UI --> User : 3D-Ansicht interaktiv nutzbar

@enduml